  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Pero is Puss 'n Boots of storybook fame and he's caught up in a whirlwind adventure, traveling through time and around the world! True-blue Pero has been \"cat-apulted\" back through time by the terrible Count Gruemon. Now Pero must cross many dangerous lands to defeat Count Gruemon and recover the Time Machine which will return Pero home. It's a \"cat-astrophe!\"",
